      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Now return to the application.\n- This is where all of that work shows up for the business.\n- Start in Waypoint with invoices already classified as matched, variance, and disputed.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the Waypoint invoices tab. Show a list of invoices with visible statuses and totals at the top.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111154_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.11.27@2x.png"
    },
    {
