        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "- Start with one that matched cleanly.\n- The point is not just that it was approved.\n- The point is that Waypoint can show why it should be paid.\n- Bring up the evidence behind that decision.",
      "demo_actions": "Open a matched invoice. Walk through invoice lines, contract terms, receipt context, batch records, QA release, milestone status, and approval history.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111259_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.12.21@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
        "time": false,
        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- Then compare that with one that does not line up.\n- Waypoint makes the gap easy to see.\n- It ties the issue back to the source record.\n- Now the team can review the invoice from facts instead of email threads and manual checks.",
      "demo_actions": "Open a variance or disputed invoice. Highlight the mismatch and the linked evidence behind the decision.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111347_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.13.26@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
        "time": false,
        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Once you have that evidence trail, the rollup matters more.\n- This is about dollars, not just flags.\n- Show what is ready to pay, what needs review, and where risk is building.",
      "demo_actions": "Return to the invoice list. Point to dollar amounts tied to matched, variance, and disputed invoices. Sort or filter to surface high-value exceptions.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111253_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.11.27@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
        "time": false,
        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "- And this scales beyond one invoice at a time.\n- Waypoint can run the same checks across the full set.\n- Every invoice is held to the same standard.\n- Every decision is tied back to the same evidence chain.",
      "demo_actions": "Kick off a batch reconciliation or return to a completed run. Show the enabled IQs and the progress or result summary.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111427_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.14.06@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
